#### 6.2 Admin Dashboard

**Template:** `course/templates/course/adminpage/admin_dashboard.html`

**Description:** Dashboard for administrative functions.

**Data Context:**
- `users`: List of user objects
- `courses`: List of course objects
- `stats`: Dictionary of system statistics